Maria Darling https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Darling 0 Maria Darling (born (1964-10-23)23 October 1964) is a British voice actress who regularly provides character voices for children's television programmes in the UK and the US, as well as video games such as the Professor Layton series and the UK versions of the Ape Escape franchise.
